aS'Many people barely mention the hurricane at all.'
p5750
aS'My neighbors tell me about the city before the storm and the difficulty of evacuating.'
p5751
aS'They speak with rage about the shoddy levee system: It was the Army Corps\xe2\x80\x99s failure, not the 2005 hurricane, that flooded the city.'
p5752
aS'They talk about feeling abandoned, left to drown in the world\xe2\x80\x99s most powerful country.'
p5753
aS'They mourn the loss of family members and friends.'
p5754
