aS"\xc2\xa0The FBI's\xc2\xa0annual report on violent crime statistics\xc2\xa0released Monday\xc2\xa0tracked a growing priority of\xc2\xa0the Trump administration, which has offered ominous warnings since Inauguration Day of a growing crime problem in America and a re-emergence of violent criminal gangs."
