aS'She criticized the Obama administration\xe2\x80\x99s approach to handling campus sexual assault, including its suggestion in a 2011   that schools use a "preponderance of evidence" standard \xe2\x80\x94 the same one used for other student discipline matters and in civil trials, but looser than the one used in the criminal justice system \xe2\x80\x94 in evaluating sexual assault cases.'
