aS'Curiously, the Dutch researchers also found that those who couldn\xe2\x80\x99t resist the urge to do a little work while on vacation were no less likely to reap the benefits than those who avoided all work.'
p10271
aS'So no need to banish your phones entirely.'
p10272
aS'Perhaps the key to enjoyment on vacation is the ability to control what you do, and to do what is most natural to you.'
p10273
aS'Workaholics might find "enforced" relaxation stressful.'
p10274
aS'By all means let them work a little on vacation!'
