aS'In short, the same behavior that they had engaged in with impunity.'
p11212
aS'This month, Senator Al Franken, Democrat of Minnesota,   his blue slip for David Stras, a well-respected but very conservative justice on the state\xe2\x80\x99s Supreme Court whom Mr. Trump nominated to the Court of Appeals for the Eighth Circuit.'
