aS'Unlike their Republican counterparts, however, these Democrats provided a clear explanation for their opposition: The White House, they said, made no meaningful effort to consult with them before making nominations.'
p11215
aS'Mr. Wyden and Mr. Merkley said Mr. Trump had completely bypassed Oregon\xe2\x80\x99s well-established bipartisan selection committee.'
