p14584
aS'The fight against malaria has reached a critical moment.'
p14585
aS'We now face the prospect of a resurgence of the disease.'
p14586
aS'Strains that are resistant to multiple drugs have appeared in Southeast Asia, and could spread to Africa, where they have the potential to cause a deadly catastrophe.'
