aS'The latest Republican stab at overhauling the Affordable Care Act manages to be both more timid and more sweeping than previous efforts to replace Obamacare.'
p15678
aS'Known as Graham-Cassidy, it was written by a quartet of Republican senators led by Lindsey Graham of South Carolina and Bill Cassidy of Louisiana.'
p15679
aS'In the timid sense, the proposal would keep much more of Obamacare\xe2\x80\x99s taxes and spending in place than previous Republican plans this year.'
